subject: Luge Racing
lead_paragraph: The Olympic and world champion Armin Zoggeler earned his 55th title and led an Italian sweep of the men’s luge World Cup event in Lake Placid, N.Y.
snippet: The Olympic and world champion Armin Zoggeler earned his 55th title and led an Italian sweep of the men’s luge World Cup event in Lake Placid, N.Y.
